Description :
        "Hold me a lot today too" "Yuki-chan...!!!!!"Haru and Yuki are childhood friends and are currently lovingly living together.Even though we've been closer than anyone since we were little and have been together for such a long time, our love for each other is bottomless.I want to be tight, and I want to have sex!However, there were many conflicts before they came here... We will deliver the precious daily life of these two in full emotional style.
